OL,3,CMother and brother in court over
OL,4,Cteenage girl's death in house fire
OL,6,FThe mother and brother of a teenager
OL,7,Fwho died in a house fire have appeared
OL,8,Fin court charged with manslaughter and
OL,9,Fabstracting electricity.
OL,11,FLeah Casson, 18, died in a blaze at
OL,12,Fher home in Vicarage Street, North
OL,13,FShields, North Tyneside, on 16 January
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FHer mother Danielle Johnson, 43, and
OL,17,Fbrother Louis Casson, 19, appeared at
OL,18,FNorth Tyneside Magistrates' Court on
OL,19,FThursday (8 January) where they spoke
OL,20,Fto confirm their name, age and address.
