OL,4,Cteenage girl's death in house fire
OL,6,FThey are both charged with
OL,7,Fmanslaughter and the mother faces two
OL,8,Fcounts of abstracting electricity
OL,9,Fwhile her son faces one count.
OL,11,FCo-accused Craig Watson, 42, appeared
OL,12,Fvia a video link. He is also charged
OL,13,Fwith manslaughter and two counts of
OL,14,Fabstracting electricity.
OL,16,FCalvin Smith, 37, of North Tyneside,
OL,17,Fdid not enter pleas to the two charges
OL,18,Fof abstracting electricity that he
OL,19,Ffaces. He is not charged with killing
OL,20,Fthe teenager.
