OL,4,Cteenage girl's death in house fire
OL,6,FAll four defendants were granted
OL,7,Funconditional bail to appear at
OL,8,FNewcastle Crown Court on 10 February.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police initially treated
OL,11,Fthe fire as arson, and at the time Ms
OL,12,FCasson's loved ones paid tribute,
OL,13,Fsaying: "Leah was an outgoing, bubbly
OL,14,Fyoung woman who we loved so much and
OL,15,Fwe can't believe she has gone.
OL,17,F"Please let us grieve for her as a
OL,18,Ffamily and respect our privacy at this
OL,19,Ftime."
